{
  "id": 44,
  "nameSimple": "Ad-Dukhan",
  "nameArabic": "الدخان",
  "versesCount": 59,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 4415,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "44:1",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " حمٓ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99925,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Ḥā, Meem.<sup foot_note=229628>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751128,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "哈一，米目。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4416,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "44:2",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلْكِتَـٰبِ ٱلْمُبِينِ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99835,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "By the clear Book,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751129,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以明确的经典盟誓，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4417,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "44:3",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّآ أَنزَلْنَـٰهُ فِى لَيْلَةٍ مُّبَـٰرَكَةٍ ۚ إِنَّا كُنَّا مُنذِرِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99942,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We sent it down during a blessed night.<sup foot_note=229629>1</sup> Indeed, We were to warn [mankind].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751130,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在一个吉祥的夜间，我确已降示它，我确是警告者。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4418,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "44:4",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فِيهَا يُفْرَقُ كُلُّ أَمْرٍ حَكِيمٍ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99954,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Therein [i.e., on that night] is made distinct<sup foot_note=229632>1</sup> every precise matter -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751131,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那夜里，一切睿智的事，都被判定，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4419,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "44:5",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَمْرًا مِّنْ عِندِنَآ ۚ إِنَّا كُنَّا مُرْسِلِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99966,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Every] matter [proceeding] from Us. Indeed, We were to send [a messenger]",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751132,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那是按照从我那里发出的命令的。我确是派遣使者的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4420,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "44:6",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "رَحْمَةً مِّن رَّبِّكَ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ ٱلسَّمِيعُ ٱلْعَلِيمُ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99978,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "As mercy from your Lord. Indeed, He is the Hearing, the Knowing,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751133,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那是由于从你的主发出的恩惠。他确是全聪的，确是全知的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4421,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "44:7",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "رَبِّ ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَآ ۖ إِن كُنتُم مُّوقِنِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99980,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Lord of the heavens and the earth and that between them, if you would be certain.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751134,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他是天地万物的之主，如果你们是坚信者。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4422,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "44:8",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "لَآ إِلَـٰهَ إِلَّا هُوَ يُحْىِۦ وَيُمِيتُ ۖ رَبُّكُمْ وَرَبُّ ءَابَآئِكُمُ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99982,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "There is no deity except Him; He gives life and causes death. [He is] your Lord and the Lord of your first forefathers.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751135,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "除他外，绝无应受崇拜的。他能使死者生，能使生者死，他是你们的主，也是你们祖先的主。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4423,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "44:9",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "بَلْ هُمْ فِى شَكٍّ يَلْعَبُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99984,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But they are in doubt, amusing themselves.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751136,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "不然，他们是在疑惑中的，是游戏的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4424,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "44:10",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَٱرْتَقِبْ يَوْمَ تَأْتِى ٱلسَّمَآءُ بِدُخَانٍ مُّبِينٍ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99926,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then watch for the Day when the sky will bring a visible smoke",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751137,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你应当等待烟雾漫天的日子，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4425,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "44:11",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَغْشَى ٱلنَّاسَ ۖ هَـٰذَا عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99927,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Covering the people; this is a painful torment.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751138,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那烟雾将笼罩世人，他们说：“这是一种痛苦的刑罚。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4426,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "44:12",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "رَّبَّنَا ٱكْشِفْ عَنَّا ٱلْعَذَابَ إِنَّا مُؤْمِنُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99928,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[They will say], \"Our Lord, remove from us the torment; indeed, we are believers.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751139,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我们的主啊！求你为我们解除这种刑罚，我们确是信道的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4427,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "44:13",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَنَّىٰ لَهُمُ ٱلذِّكْرَىٰ وَقَدْ جَآءَهُمْ رَسُولٌ مُّبِينٌ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99929,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "How will there be for them a reminder [at that time]? And there had come to them a clear Messenger.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751140,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们怎能觉悟呢？显赫的使者，确已来临他们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4428,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "44:14",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ تَوَلَّوْا۟ عَنْهُ وَقَالُوا۟ مُعَلَّمٌ مَّجْنُونٌ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99930,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then they turned away from him and said, \"[He was] taught [and is] a madman.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751141,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "而他们却鄙弃他。他们说：他是受教的，是疯狂的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4429,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "44:15",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّا كَاشِفُوا۟ ٱلْعَذَابِ قَلِيلًا ۚ إِنَّكُمْ عَآئِدُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99931,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We will remove the torment for a little. Indeed, you [disbelievers] will return [to disbelief].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751142,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我必定要暂时解除这种刑罚，你们必定复返于悖逆。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4430,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "44:16",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 198,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ نَبْطِشُ ٱلْبَطْشَةَ ٱلْكُبْرَىٰٓ إِنَّا مُنتَقِمُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99932,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The Day We will strike with the greatest assault, indeed, We will take retribution.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751143,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我进行最大的袭击之日，我必定要惩罚他们。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4431,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "44:17",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "۞ وَلَقَدْ فَتَنَّا قَبْلَهُمْ قَوْمَ فِرْعَوْنَ وَجَآءَهُمْ رَسُولٌ كَرِيمٌ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99933,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We had already tried before them the people of Pharaoh, and there came to them a noble messenger [i.e., Moses],",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751144,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在他们之前，我确已考验了法老的百姓。有一个高贵的使者来临他们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4432,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "44:18",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَنْ أَدُّوٓا۟ إِلَىَّ عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ۖ إِنِّى لَكُمْ رَسُولٌ أَمِينٌ",
      "pageNumber": 496,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99934,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Saying], \"Render to me the servants of Allāh.<sup foot_note=229641>1</sup> Indeed, I am to you a trustworthy messenger,\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751145,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "说：“你们把安拉的仆人们交给我吧！我确是一个忠实的使者，奉命来教化你们的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4433,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "44:19",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَأَن لَّا تَعْلُوا۟ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ ۖ إِنِّىٓ ءَاتِيكُم بِسُلْطَـٰنٍ مُّبِينٍ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99935,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And [saying], \"Be not haughty with Allāh. Indeed, I have come to you with clear evidence.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751146,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你们不要对安拉高傲。我必定要昭示你们一个明证。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4434,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "verseKey": "44:20",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِنِّى عُذْتُ بِرَبِّى وَرَبِّكُمْ أَن تَرْجُمُونِ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99593,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And indeed, I have sought refuge in my Lord and your Lord, lest you stone me.<sup foot_note=229642>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751147,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已求庇于我的主和你们的主，免遭你们的谋害。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4435,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "verseKey": "44:21",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِن لَّمْ تُؤْمِنُوا۟ لِى فَٱعْتَزِلُونِ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99661,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But if you do not believe me, then leave me alone.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751148,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "如果你们不相信我，那么，你们放任我吧！”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4436,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "verseKey": "44:22",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَدَعَا رَبَّهُۥٓ أَنَّ هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ قَوْمٌ مُّجْرِمُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99937,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And [finally] he called to his Lord that these were a criminal people.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751149,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他就祈祷他的主说：这等人，确是犯罪的民众。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4437,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "verseKey": "44:23",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَأَسْرِ بِعِبَادِى لَيْلًا إِنَّكُم مُّتَّبَعُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99553,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Allāh said], \"Then set out with My servants by night. Indeed, you are to be pursued.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751150,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "（主说）：你带着我的众仆在夜间出走吧！你们必定要被追赶。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4438,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "verseKey": "44:24",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱتْرُكِ ٱلْبَحْرَ رَهْوًا ۖ إِنَّهُمْ جُندٌ مُّغْرَقُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99595,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And leave the sea in stillness.<sup foot_note=229645>1</sup> Indeed, they are an army to be drowned.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751151,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你让海水保持平静，他们必定是被淹死的军队。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4439,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "verseKey": "44:25",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَمْ تَرَكُوا۟ مِن جَنَّـٰتٍ وَعُيُونٍ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99375,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "How much they left behind of gardens and springs",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751152,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们曾抛下若干园圃和泉源，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4440,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "verseKey": "44:26",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَزُرُوعٍ وَمَقَامٍ كَرِيمٍ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99476,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And crops and noble sites",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751153,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "庄稼和美宅，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4441,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "verseKey": "44:27",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَنَعْمَةٍ كَانُوا۟ فِيهَا فَـٰكِهِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99938,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And comfort wherein they were amused.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751154,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以及他们所享受的福泽！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4442,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "verseKey": "44:28",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَذَٰلِكَ ۖ وَأَوْرَثْنَـٰهَا قَوْمًا ءَاخَرِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99939,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Thus. And We caused to inherit it another people.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751155,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "结局是这样的：我曾使别的民众继承他们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4443,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "verseKey": "44:29",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 433,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَمَا بَكَتْ عَلَيْهِمُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ وَٱلْأَرْضُ وَمَا كَانُوا۟ مُنظَرِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99940,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And the heaven and earth wept not for them, nor were they reprieved.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751156,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "天地没有哭他们，他们也没有获得缓刑。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4444,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "verseKey": "44:30",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَلَقَدْ نَجَّيْنَا بَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ مِنَ ٱلْعَذَابِ ٱلْمُهِينِ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99943,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We certainly saved the Children of Israel from the humiliating torment -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751157,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已使以色列的后裔摆脱了凌辱的刑罚--",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4445,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "verseKey": "44:31",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مِن فِرْعَوْنَ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ عَالِيًا مِّنَ ٱلْمُسْرِفِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99944,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "From Pharaoh. Indeed, he was a haughty one among the transgressors.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751158,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "法老的刑罚。他确是高傲的，确是过分的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4446,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "verseKey": "44:32",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَلَقَدِ ٱخْتَرْنَـٰهُمْ عَلَىٰ عِلْمٍ عَلَى ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99945,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We certainly chose them by knowledge over [all] the worlds.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751159,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已本真知而选拔他们，使他们超轶各民族，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4447,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "verseKey": "44:33",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَءَاتَيْنَـٰهُم مِّنَ ٱلْـَٔايَـٰتِ مَا فِيهِ بَلَـٰٓؤٌا۟ مُّبِينٌ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99946,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We gave them of signs that in which there was a clear trial.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751160,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我赏赐他们许多迹象，都是有明显的试验的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4448,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "verseKey": "44:34",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ لَيَقُولُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99947,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, these [disbelievers] are saying,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751161,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这等人必定要说：",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4449,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "verseKey": "44:35",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنْ هِىَ إِلَّا مَوْتَتُنَا ٱلْأُولَىٰ وَمَا نَحْنُ بِمُنشَرِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99948,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "\"There is not but our first death, and we will not be resurrected.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751162,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "“我们只有初次的死亡，我们不会复活。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4450,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "verseKey": "44:36",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَأْتُوا۟ بِـَٔابَآئِنَآ إِن كُنتُمْ صَـٰدِقِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99949,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then bring [back] our forefathers, if you should be truthful.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751163,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你们把我们的祖先召唤回来吧，如果你们是说实话的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4451,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "verseKey": "44:37",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَهُمْ خَيْرٌ أَمْ قَوْمُ تُبَّعٍ وَٱلَّذِينَ مِن قَبْلِهِمْ ۚ أَهْلَكْنَـٰهُمْ ۖ إِنَّهُمْ كَانُوا۟ مُجْرِمِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99950,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Are they better or the people of Tubbaʿ<sup foot_note=229648>1</sup> and those before them? We destroyed them, [for] indeed, they were criminals.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751164,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们是更高贵的呢？还是图白的宗族是更高贵呢？在他们之前的许多民族，我已加以毁灭了；因为他们确是犯罪者。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4452,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "verseKey": "44:38",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَا خَلَقْنَا ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَا لَـٰعِبِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99951,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We did not create the heavens and earth and that between them in play.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751165,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我没有以游戏的态度创造天地万物，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4453,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "verseKey": "44:39",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَا خَلَقْنَـٰهُمَآ إِلَّا بِٱلْحَقِّ وَلَـٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَهُمْ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 497,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99952,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "We did not create them except in truth, but most of them do not know.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751166,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我只本真理而创造之，但他们大半不知道。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4454,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "verseKey": "44:40",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ يَوْمَ ٱلْفَصْلِ مِيقَـٰتُهُمْ أَجْمَعِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99955,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, the Day of Judgement is the appointed time for them all -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751167,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "甄别日，确是为他们全体预定的日期。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4455,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "verseKey": "44:41",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ لَا يُغْنِى مَوْلًى عَن مَّوْلًى شَيْـًٔا وَلَا هُمْ يُنصَرُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99956,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The Day when no relation<sup foot_note=229649>1</sup> will avail a relation at all, nor will they be helped -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751168,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，朋友对于朋友，毫无裨益，他们也不蒙援助；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4456,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "verseKey": "44:42",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 434,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِلَّا مَن رَّحِمَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ ٱلْعَزِيزُ ٱلرَّحِيمُ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99957,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Except those [believers] on whom Allāh has mercy. Indeed, He is the Exalted in Might, the Merciful.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751169,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "惟安拉所怜恤者则不然。他确是万能的，确是至慈的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4457,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "verseKey": "44:43",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ شَجَرَتَ ٱلزَّقُّومِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99958,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, the tree of zaqqūm",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751170,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "攒楛木的果实，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4458,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "verseKey": "44:44",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "طَعَامُ ٱلْأَثِيمِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99959,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Is food for the sinful.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751171,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "确是罪人的食品，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4459,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "verseKey": "44:45",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَٱلْمُهْلِ يَغْلِى فِى ٱلْبُطُونِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99960,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Like murky oil, it boils within bellies",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751172,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "像油脚样在他们的腹中沸腾，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4460,
      "verseNumber": 46,
      "verseKey": "44:46",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَغَلْىِ ٱلْحَمِيمِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99961,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Like the boiling of scalding water.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751173,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "像开水一样地沸腾。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4461,
      "verseNumber": 47,
      "verseKey": "44:47",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "خُذُوهُ فَٱعْتِلُوهُ إِلَىٰ سَوَآءِ ٱلْجَحِيمِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99962,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[It will be commanded], \"Seize him and drag him into the midst of the Hellfire,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751174,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "（主说）：“你们捉住他，然后，把他拖入火狱中，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4462,
      "verseNumber": 48,
      "verseKey": "44:48",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ صُبُّوا۟ فَوْقَ رَأْسِهِۦ مِنْ عَذَابِ ٱلْحَمِيمِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99963,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then pour over his head from the torment of scalding water.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751175,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后，再把沸水的刑罚倾注在他的头上！ ”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4463,
      "verseNumber": 49,
      "verseKey": "44:49",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ذُقْ إِنَّكَ أَنتَ ٱلْعَزِيزُ ٱلْكَرِيمُ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99964,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[It will be said], \"Taste! Indeed, you are the honored, the noble!<sup foot_note=229650>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751176,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你尝试吧！你确是显赫的，确是尊贵的！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4464,
      "verseNumber": 50,
      "verseKey": "44:50",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ هَـٰذَا مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تَمْتَرُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99967,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, this is what you used to dispute.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751177,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这（刑罚）确是你们生前所怀疑的。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4465,
      "verseNumber": 51,
      "verseKey": "44:51",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ فِى مَقَامٍ أَمِينٍ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99968,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, the righteous will be in a secure place:",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751178,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "敬畏者必定要住在安全的地方--",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4466,
      "verseNumber": 52,
      "verseKey": "44:52",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فِى جَنَّـٰتٍ وَعُيُونٍ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99969,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Within gardens and springs,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751179,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这里有园圃和源泉，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4467,
      "verseNumber": 53,
      "verseKey": "44:53",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَلْبَسُونَ مِن سُندُسٍ وَإِسْتَبْرَقٍ مُّتَقَـٰبِلِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99970,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Wearing [garments of] fine silk and brocade, facing each other.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751180,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "穿着绫罗绸缎，相向而坐。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4468,
      "verseNumber": 54,
      "verseKey": "44:54",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَذَٰلِكَ وَزَوَّجْنَـٰهُم بِحُورٍ عِينٍ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99971,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Thus. And We will marry them to fair women with large, [beautiful] eyes.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751181,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "结局是这样的：我将以白皙的、美目的女子，做他们的伴侣。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4469,
      "verseNumber": 55,
      "verseKey": "44:55",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَدْعُونَ فِيهَا بِكُلِّ فَـٰكِهَةٍ ءَامِنِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99972,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "They will call therein for every [kind of] fruit - safe and secure.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751182,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们在乐园中，将安全地索取各种水果。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4470,
      "verseNumber": 56,
      "verseKey": "44:56",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "لَا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا ٱلْمَوْتَ إِلَّا ٱلْمَوْتَةَ ٱلْأُولَىٰ ۖ وَوَقَىٰهُمْ عَذَابَ ٱلْجَحِيمِ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99973,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "They will not taste death therein except the first death, and He will have protected them from the punishment of Hellfire",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751183,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们在乐园中，除初次死亡外不再尝死的滋味。安拉将使他们得免于火狱的刑罚。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4471,
      "verseNumber": 57,
      "verseKey": "44:57",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَضْلًا مِّن رَّبِّكَ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ هُوَ ٱلْفَوْزُ ٱلْعَظِيمُ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99974,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "As bounty from your Lord. That is what is the great attainment.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751184,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那是由于你的主的恩典，那确是伟大的成功。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4472,
      "verseNumber": 58,
      "verseKey": "44:58",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَإِنَّمَا يَسَّرْنَـٰهُ بِلِسَانِكَ لَعَلَّهُمْ يَتَذَكَّرُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99975,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And indeed, We have eased it [i.e., the Qur’ān] in your tongue that they might be reminded.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751185,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我以你的语言，使《古兰经》成为易解的，只为希望他们能觉悟。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4473,
      "verseNumber": 59,
      "verseKey": "44:59",
      "hizbNumber": 50,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 199,
      "rukuNumber": 435,
      "manzilNumber": 6,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَٱرْتَقِبْ إِنَّهُم مُّرْتَقِبُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 498,
      "juzNumber": 25,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 99976,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So watch, [O Muḥammad]; indeed, they are watching [for your end].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751186,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你等着吧，他们确是等待着的！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}